This page allows you to submit your papers to CoMa. The form consists of the following elements: the title field (this has to be filled out), a field for a short abstract, a subform for the names of your co-authors, a subform for the topics your paper is about (here you select from a list of topics the conference is about). When you are finished with the form, click 'add paper' to submit the information. In case you deceide not to submit your paper at this time click 'cancel'.
